works.description:
This blogger has already had this
material  
removed for copyright. As a professional wrestler I had promotional  
pictures taken which were my own property. Paid for by myself and all  
reproduction of any picture was done with my consent. This blogger does
not  
have permission to use any pictures of me. He also has a picture along
with  
others that have been altered. One with my head shot on another body with 

BNP leader Nick Griffin. If you scroll down the whole article you will see
 
other pictures where the same has been done....the original picture I had 

crutches. This was taken illegally in Lincoln County Court by Michael
Brown  
and given to Barking spider. There is a clear sign in the Magistrates
court  
that "No pictures are to be taken past the entrance doors". If you notice 

the right hand side of the picture has been cut. That is because it shows 

clearly the waiting area in LCC. I have reported this to the Magistrates, 

the police are involved, and I have supplied them with copies of that  
picture and the others where they just use my head.
He has also posted the video without permission from myself or the TV   
network on the following site
